GudERP — School ERP ProductDocument (Investor-Ready)
Document purpose & audience
GudERP is a School ERP platform designed to digitize and streamline day-to-dayschool operations while improving transparency for parents and reducingadministrative load for teachers. This document is written for investors, schoolleadership, and internal product/engineering teams.
Product overview
Introduction to GudERP
GudERP is a role-based School ERP system delivered through a web panel andmobile apps. It centralizes student records, attendance, academics, assignments,communication, fee operations, and institutional reporting into a unified platform.
GudERP is built to work for a broad range of schools—from small privateinstitutions to multi-campus groups—by offering:
A configurable structure for classes/sections/subjects
Bulk data operations for fast onboarding
Clear workflows for daily operations
Parent-facing transparency and alerts
Vision
To become the trusted operating system for schools by providing an easy-to-adopt, reliable, and scalable platform that improves learning operations and parentengagement.
