Mission
Digitize core school processes with minimal complexity.
Improve operational efficiency for school administration and teachers.
Provide parents with accurate, real-time visibility into attendance, academicprogress, and fees.
Establish a secure foundation for future extensions (payments, transport,analytics, integrations).
Problems GudERP solves
Schools often operate with fragmented processes and inconsistent recordkeeping. GudERP addresses:
Paper-based or spreadsheet-heavy student data and attendance
Delayed academic reporting and manual consolidation of marks
Inefficient assignment distribution and tracking
Unstructured communication across admin, teachers, and parents
Fee management complexity (structures, installments, challans, pending dues)
High dependency on a few staff members for reporting and compliance
Limited parent visibility leading to trust gaps and repeated follow-ups
Key benefits
Digitization: Central repository for student and academic records
Transparency: Parents can view attendance, marks, and fee status withoutrepeated calls/visits
Efficiency: Reduced manual work through bulk upload, templates, andstandardized workflows
Accountability: Audit-friendly tracking of entries (attendance, marks, fees)
Decision support: Reports and analytics for leadership to identify trends early
